race.comment: MYSTIC ART (6) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 20.20 beating BARRY THE BOSS. Looks to have an edge on most of these. SOMERSET BLUEY (7) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 20.26 beating SLEEK ASSASSIN. Will go close again if runs up to latest. SLEEK ASSASSIN (8) was in the money again last time and not beaten far when second (20.39) at this track in a Grade 6/MDN. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. GRAPHITE (1) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.
